headline: Dow Jones Acquires WorldECR to Enhance Editorial Coverage for Global Compliance Community
summary: Dow Jones today announced it has acquired WorldECR, an industry-leading provider of news, data and analysis on global export control and trade sanctions. This is the latest in a series of investments and acquisitions aimed at bolstering Dow Jones's portfolio of specialized news, data, analysis and events for business users.
